text: H-Town most commonly refers to the city of Houston, Texas. (see also: Nicknames of Houston#H-Town) H-Town may also refer to: ==Nicknames== * Houston, Texas *Hughson, California *Hamilton, Ontario *Hollister, California * Hamilton, Ohio *Hartford, Michigan *Hamilton, New Zealand ==Other uses== * H-Town (band), a R&B; music group active from 1990s to present * H-Town (publisher), a Finnish magazine publisher
title: H-Town
